exercise.name: Rotational Side Plank
exercise.description: Position your left elbow beneath your left shoulder.  Stack your feet together and bridge up off of the ground.  While holding strong with your body in a straight line, rotate and wrap your right arm underneath your body.  Reach back up to the ceiling
